                                                                   Excel part 6
                                                                 
                                                                 VBA Macros
                                                                 
                                                              Step 1: Install developer tab
                                                              
                                                   Go to file -> options -> Customize Ribbons -> developer tab (tick)
                                                   Go to developer, record macro.
                                                   Use relative referencing for recording macros for relative positions.
                                                   Save as excel-macro-enabled-notebook.
                                                   
                                                   Personalization is possible in excel.
                                                    
                                                    
                                                   References: Coursera Everyday excel, CU Boulder
                                                            
